description: Worshippers pay their respects to the head of the Serbian Orthodox Church, who died with Covid-19.
title: Serbia: Thousands mourn Patriarch Irinej amid Covid concerns
title_page: Serbia: Thousands mourn Patriarch Irinej amid Covid concerns - BBC News
maintext: He is thought to have contracted the disease at the funeral of the Church's most senior cleric in Montenegro, 82-year-old Metropolitan Bishop Amfilohije Radovic, who also died of Covid-19 earlier this month.
